data.description: Location, Location Location!!!! Welcome home to 129 Tirzah Road, York, SC 29745.  This quaint 1940's home features 3 bed/2 full baths, w/one bedroom is large with a wood fireplace, kitchen w/updated countertops and stainless-steel appliances, breakfast area and laundry room. Enjoy your morning coffee on the covered front porch admiring the beautiful flowers that bloom in the spring (see pictures) or hang out with family on the screened in porch making memories.  The 28 X 33 wired outbuilding is a great space for additional storage and being is sold AS IS. Just a short commute to Rock Hill, York, Lake Wylie and Clover, dining, shopping and entertainment.
